    "side_effects_description": "The possible side effect of using Cynara scolymus are numerous and can be severe when used improperly. Cynara scolymus may interact with medications such as blood thinners, diabetes medications, and blood pressure medications, which can lead to serious complications. Improper use of Cynara scolymus can also exacerbate diarrhea in individuals with pre-existing gastrointestinal conditions, and in some cases, induce diarrhea in healthy individuals, causing dehydration and electrolyte imbalances. The excessive consumption of Cynara scolymus can lead to gastrointestinal symptoms, including diarrhea, which can be uncomfortable and potentially debilitating. Furthermore, Cynara scolymus may worsen diarrhea in individuals with conditions such as irritable bowel syndrome, inflammatory bowel disease, and gastroenteritis."
